snippet.title: Top 10 Fastest 0-60 Cars Under 300HP in Forza Horizon 5 | Top Acceleration Cars
snippet.description:
These are the top 10 fastest quickest  0-100km/h cars that comes below 300hp in Forza Horizon 5. Even though it's not too much of Horsepower, they're surprisingly pretty fast and quick which will be perfect for drag races. As well as 0 to 100, it will be tested that how long does it take to reach 0-200km/h of speed. 

🔹️GTA VC DE Monect Layout: https://bit.ly/3pGeEPD
🔹️ETS 2 Monect Layout: https://bit.ly/RDL-4938

The list starts from the lowest Horsepower to the highest and the current time ranking of each tested vehicle is also indicated all the time. So it will be always informative. Who's the Quickest little beast? Let's find out!

00:05 - Ariel Nomad 236HP
00:28 - Alphine A110 248HP
00:53 - Exomotive Exocet 252HP
01:39 - Caterham Superlight 263HP
01:57 - Subaru Impreza 276HP
02:31 - Mazda RX-7 276HP
02:57 - BAC Mono 280HP
03:13 - Peugeot 207 Super 2K 280HP
03:36 - Ford Super Van 3 295HP
03:56 - KTM X-Bow R 295HP
04:18 - Final Results
